{
  "id": "adv_card_yu_05_02",
  "title": "鈴村優 2話 うちの初めての人",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-living-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_living-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3d_corridor_evening",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "鈴村さん、どこだ！　いたら返事をしてくれ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san‚ where are you? Please respond if you're there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3621.4966138,
          "startTime": 4.4214966138
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu001.m4a",
      "text": "あはは……顔、熱いなぁ……体は寒いのに……\nあれ？　薬、どこにやったっけ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha… My face is feelin' hot… but my body feels cold…\nHuh? Where did I put them meds…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "寮にいたのか、良かった。薬は俺が持って来るから\n休んでてくれ……って、凄い汗じゃないか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were at the dorm‚ huh? That's a relief. I'll bring the meds for you.\nTake a rest… Oh‚ you're sweating a lot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　……{user}さん……？\n……あれ？　なんで寮にいるん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hm?… {user}-san…?\n…Huh? Why are you at the dorm…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.9629580411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "時間になっても鈴村さんが現場に来ないって聞いたんだ\nそれで俺が様子を見に来たんだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard that you didn't make it to the venue on time.\nThat's why I came to check on you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 37.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……現場……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… The venue…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.3186621666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "……あーっ！？　もうこんな時間やんか！\nあかん、ぼーっとしてもうた！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah! It's already this late!\nDarn it‚ I got lost in thought!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "大遅刻や！　{user}さん\n今すぐタクシー呼んで、うちを連れてって！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm super late! {user}-san‚\nCall a taxi right away and take me there!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もちろん連れて行くつもりだ\nただし、ファン交流イベントじゃなく、病院にだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sure‚ I'll make sure to take you there.\nBut‚ it's not for the fan interaction event‚ it's for the hospital.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 63.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 63.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "単なる風邪で安心したよ\n調子はどうだ？　苦しくないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm relieved that it's just a common cold.\nHow are you feeling? Are you experiencing any discomfort?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 69.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "点滴打ったら、だいぶ良くなりました\n{user}さん、ご迷惑おかけしました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After receiving the IV drip‚ I've improved quite a bit.\nI apologize for the trouble I've caused you‚ {user}-san.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "……でな？　これだけ良くなったら\n今からイベントに出られると思うんやけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ considering how much better I am now‚\nI think I can participate in the event.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 83.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ダメだ。今日の鈴村優の仕事は、部屋で一日オフだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No‚ that's not possible. Today‚ Suzumura-san‚ you have the day off in your room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 89.2333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "ちょ、ちょっと、待って下さい！\nそんなん、瑠依ちゃんとすみれちゃんに申し訳ないです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ please! I feel bad for Rui-chan and Sumire-chan about this.\nI'm sorry to them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "天動さんと奥山さんには、状況はもう伝えてある\n絶対に休ませてくれ、だそうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tendo-san and Okuyama-san have already been informed about the situation.\nThey insist that you must take a break‚ no matter what.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃん達を先に味方につけるなんて\n{user}さん、せこいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Winning over Rui-chan and Sumire-chan first‚ huh?\n{user}-san‚ you're so cunning.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 106.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "こうでもしないと絶対に行こうとするだろ。担当\nアイドルが倒れるところはもう二度と見たくないんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to do it this way‚ otherwise you would definitely try to go.\nI don't want to see an idol collapse ever again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 116.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu010.m4a",
      "text": "あ……\nそれって、もしかして麻奈さんの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah…\nCould it be because of Mana-san's…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 121.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "今の鈴村さんは、休むべきだ\nメンバーのためにも、ファンのためにも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzumura-san‚ you should rest now.\nFor the sake of the members and the fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu011.m4a",
      "text": "……分かりました\nうちが、甘かったです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I understand.\nI was too naive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hospital-02-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "hospital-02-noon",
      "startTime": 132.5666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu012.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ごめんなさい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry‚ {user}-san…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4082.998657199994,
          "startTime": 136.6496653239
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "おかゆ、作ってきたよ。味に自信はないけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made some rice porridge. I'm not confident about the taste‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 141.7333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu013.m4a",
      "text": "何から何まですみません\nこんなことまでさせてしまって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry for everything.\nI feel responsible for letting it come to this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu014.m4a",
      "text": "それもこれも、うちが自己管理出来てなかったせいです\nこれくらいなら大丈夫って、甘く見てました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's because I couldn't manage myself properly.\nI underestimated things‚ thinking I would be fine with just this.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 152.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 156.4
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "speakerNameEn": "Yu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02/sud_vo_adv_card_yu_05_02-yu015.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは\nあんなに心配してくれはったのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san…\nYou were so worried…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoyuroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoyuroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 160.8666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
